      "comment": "BRONELLY TIMMY (3) has a strong record this track and trip including two wins from four starts. Was out of the placings last time (25.31) at this track in a T3 Grade 6, finishing eighth and beaten 11 lengths. Makes strong appeal on best. IVORY RAMEN (7) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (24.87) in a T3 Grade 6 at this track. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. BAKALI SURPRISE (8) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten 0.8 lengths, (24.70) at this track. Can measure up. YANKEE BLOOD (1) is another with top-three prospects.",
